data.description: Welcome home! You have found the one. This 3 bedroom, 1 bathroom home has so many updates on top of the charm and character it has to offer. Enter the home into the living room, off of the living room is a screened in porch which leads to the large fenced in backyard. Enjoy summer nights in this beautiful backyard, with a privacy fence blocking the street view. The shed has a new roof from 2023! Back inside, check out the kitchen! There are plenty of cabinets to store all you'll need. The kitchen has a new sink and faucet plus new tile backsplash! The basement has a great bonus space that can be used as an office space or bonus room. New drywall and laminate flooring! The home has been freshly painted throughout and a new garage door 2024! The owners have taken great care in updates and maintenance of this home! Perfect location close to Snyder park, multiple highways, Springfield commons and downtown!Rely on own measurements!
